{"view":"article","slug":"skewb-lbl","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"斜转层先法"},"content":{"zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>斜转层先法</strong></p><p><strong>符号</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong>S </strong>(Sledge)<strong> = r' R r R', H </strong>(Hedge)<strong> = R r' R' r.</strong></p><p>此图中黄，红，绿面分别为U，F，R面. 每个角块上的字母表示以该角为旋转中心顺时针旋转120°。DBL角对应字母b。x,y,z表示整体顺时针旋转90°。</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>底层</strong></p><p><strong>DBL角</strong></p><p>凭直觉做底。以白底为例。称同色且相邻的心和角为箭头。选择一个有箭头的面作为底层的面，视该箭头的角已复原，并将角放在DBL。若不存在，即无连色，可通过1步转动变成前者。</p><p><strong>DFL, DBR角</strong></p><p>若UFR角是白角，则做下面的公式。</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UFR to DFL</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x B</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z r' R\">x z r' R</span></p></td><td><p><strong>x z r R</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UFR to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image11.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image13.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image15.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x r'</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x R r'\">x R r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x R' r'\">x R' r'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>否则，通过1步转动将某个白角（图中的紫色）移至UFR处后再做上面的公式。</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image17.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image19.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image21.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' / L\">R' / L</span></p></td><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>DFR角</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UBR to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image23.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image25.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image27.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x R</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x r' R r\">x r' R r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z r' R r' R'\">x z r' R r' R'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UFL to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image29.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image31.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image33.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x R'</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z R r' R'\">x z R r' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z R' r' R\">x z R' r' R</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>DFR to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image35.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image37.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image39.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z R r R' r'\">x z R r R' r'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x R' r' R r\">x R' r' R r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x r' R' r R\">x r' R' r R</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z r R r' R'\">x z r R r' R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>顶角</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image41.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Pi</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image43.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Peanut</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image45.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x H</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x z2 S\">x z2 S</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x S z' S\">x S z' S</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>顶心</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image47.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image49.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x S z2' S\">x S z2' S</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>侧心</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk16858743\"></a><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image51.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">U+</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image53.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">U-</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image55.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Z</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image57.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">H</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S z2' S\">S z2' S</span></p></td><td><p><strong>(r R' r' R) y' H</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"y' x b' S z2 r' R r\">y' x b' S z2 r' R r</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(r l' B' l) (B l r l' r)\">(r l' B' l) (B l r l' r)</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r R' r R' y L' l L' l\">r R' r R' y L' l L' l</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["x z r' R","x R r'","x R' r'","R' / L","x r' R r","x z r' R r' R'","x z R r' R'","x z R' r' R","x z R r R' r'","x R' r' R r","x r' R' r R","x z r R r' R'","x z2 S","x S z' S","x S z2' S","S z2' S","y' x b' S z2 r' R r","(r l' B' l) (B l r l' r)","r R' r R' y L' l L' l"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/skewb-lbl/zh/image1.png","warningCount":1,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
